Yoink/

# User-facing yoink output. In dev mode the server may write to repo-local
# Desktop\Yoink-style paths; ignoring these patterns prevents private
# transcripts and screenshots from accidentally landing in commits.
# Note: existing `Yoink/` entry above covers the per-topic folders
# (Desktop\Yoink\<topic>\<slug>\). On Windows NTFS git is typically
# configured with core.ignorecase=true, so a `/[A-Z]*/` pattern would
# accidentally match docs/ and extension/ too -- avoid that.
_sessions/
_all-yoinks-index.md

.claude/
